      <title>邓普顿呼吁美国国债收益率达到 5%，与摩根大通和 T. Rowe 持平</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-13/templeton-s-call-for-5-treasury-yield-matches-jpmorgan-t-rowe</link>
      <description><![CDATA[富兰克林邓普顿表示，随着美国政府增加债务供应以弥补数万亿美元的赤字，10 年期美国国债收益率可能攀升至 5% 或更高。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-13/templeton-s-call-for-5-treasury-yield-matches-jpmorgan-t-rowe</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 13 Nov 2024 04:03:18 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
